{"type":"message","id":"bfc4f5c2","parentId":"47159427","timestamp":"2026-03-04T16:35:09.473Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:23d0eb35-c732-478f-854b-b1dbc6914843 task:23d0eb35-c732-478f-854b-b1dbc6914843] 安装 GitHub 仓库：https://github.com/shinjiyu/Structured-Cognitive-Loop-Skills\n\n## 任务\n\n1. **克隆仓库**\n   ```bash\n   cd /root/.openclaw/workspace\n   git clone https://github.com/shinjiyu/Structured-Cognitive-Loop-Skills\n   ```\n\n2. **查看仓库结构**\n   - 列出目录内容\n   - 查看 README.md 了解用途\n   - 查看安装说明\n\n3. **安装依赖**\n   - 检查是否有 package.json、requirements.txt 等依赖文件\n   - 运行相应的安装命令\n\n4. **配置到 OpenClaw**\n   - 如果是 Skills 库，将其复制或链接到 skills 目录\n   - 查看是否有配置说明\n   - 按照说明进行配置\n\n5. **测试安装**\n   - 验证是否安装成功\n   - 查看可用的 Skills 或功能\n\n## 输出要求\n\n1. 仓库内容和用途说明\n2. 安装步骤和结果\n3. 如何在 OpenClaw 中使用这个库\n4. 安装后的测试结果\nCurrent time: Thursday, March 5th, 2026 — 12:35 AM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1772642109472}}
